item.title: CVE-2019-8632|2024-08-04T21:24:29.049Z -- apple -- texture-ios
item.description: Some analytics data was sent using HTTP rather than HTTPS. This was addressed by no longer sending this analytics data. This issue is fixed in Texture 5.11.10 for iOS, Texture 4.22.0.4 for Android. An attacker in a privileged network position may be able to intercept analytics data.
